Soul camp is a decent one as a 65 mage with Planar Renewal, Air pet focused with BO5/MoR can take the entire camp with no problem. There is one double pull but if you just send in HoE and burn the targeted one down you will have no problems.

The rest of the mobs in this zone with the exception of the Cragbeast Queen are also soloable by a 65 Mage. Dark Blue mobs offer 2% AA exp per kill.

