Just enter the water and hunt Reef Crusteans and Saltwater Longnose (looks like a swordfish).

Fight the mobs at their spot - will get no adds.

Reef Crusteans are slow hitters and easy, however longnoses hit hard and also backstabs so if all things go bad, dont try to outswim it, just gate. - Earthpet preferred here, no other pet can take that damage in your level.

Both mobs can drop the Talisman with manareg +1 =)<br><br><i><b>Restless</b> says:</i><br>Actually soloing even turtles at 57 is hard, 1 turtle took 80-90 % of my mana, however there are mobs in zone not listed here (yet) that will be owned by you. Summon a bunch of water breathing stones unless you have an EB item.

